0005062998130426481, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leo Cullen's side host Ulster in the quarter-finals of the BKT URC on Saturday (5pm) with a potential semi-final and final to come on the following two weekends.\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Cullen_(rugby_union)\", \"score\": 0.9654975138716163, \"rank\": 0.03573454339194619, \"text\": \"Leo Cullen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Cullen_(rugby_union)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Cullen_(rugby_union)\"}, {\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulster_Rugby\", \"score\": 0.9999999608560309, \"rank\": 3.914011770553357e-08, \"text\": \"Ulster\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulster_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulster_Rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4118519433001234e-15, \"text\": \"URC\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking last week, Leinster senior coach Jacques Nienaber said it was his \\\"understanding that he will not be available\\\".\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\", \"score\": 0.999999999984766, \"rank\": 1.307888467003936e-11, \"text\": \"Leinster\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacques_Nienaber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jacques Nienaber\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacques_Nienaber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacques_Nienaber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Farrell's Ireland side will travel to South Africa for Tests on 6 and 13 July.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Farrell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.323243638377254e-29, \"text\": \"Andy Farrell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Farrell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Farrell\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9994895444488685, \"rank\": 0.0005062998130426481, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998155306172, \"rank\": 9.769974084696122e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Men's Sevens tournament takes place at the Stade de France between 24-27 July with the squad for Paris to be named in mid-June.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 708, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999923286396, \"rank\": 7.67130220272735e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prior to that James Topping's side will compete at the Europe Sevens Championship kicking off in Croatia's Makarska next weekend and the second leg of that tournament in Hamburg at the end of the month.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Topping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Topping\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Topping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Topping\"}, {\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998643724794202, \"rank\": 0.00013564461563064922, \"text\": \"Croatia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Makarska\", \"score\": 0.9999999158724258, \"rank\": 8.41275405289917e-08, \"text\": \"Makarska\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Makarska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Makarska\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburger_SV\", \"score\": 0.9999904505708704, \"rank\": 9.445097442603413e-06, \"text\": \"Hamburg\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburger_SV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburger_SV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And talking after helping Ireland to a fifth-place finish at the HSBC SVNS Grand Final in Madrid at the weekend, Keenan suggested that he would not be returning to the province, beaten in the Champions Cup final last month, before the end of the season.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9994895444488685, \"rank\": 0.0005062998130426481, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 0.9999954596008441, \"rank\": 4.540385673743991e-06, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These opportunities do not come around too often,\\\" he said after his first Sevens appearance in five years.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to make a tough decision, but hopefully, it's one that I will not regret and I will fully commit now over the next few weeks and see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having brushed off questions about returning to Sevensin the aftermath of Antoine Dupont's switch to the code last January, the 27-year-old revealed more details of how the move came about.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antoine Dupont\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antoine_Dupont\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a very busy year for me, that's the exciting part,\\\" he said in Madrid, where France won the series.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"score\": 0.9999954596008441, \"rank\": 4.540385673743991e-06, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF\"}, {\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9827444877734809, \"rank\": 0.017558455745309703, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I suppose it was put on the table a while back but it was always going to be a bit of a last-minute decision,  \\\"I'd been injured since the Six Nations and that threw a bit of a spanner in the works.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Prior to that, I was trying to just focus on Leinster and the Champions Cup because that's where my career is and where I had to fully focus and commit 100%.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\", \"score\": 0.999999999984766, \"rank\": 1.307888467003936e-11, \"text\": \"Leinster\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leinster_Rugby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The opportunity came about pretty late on and because the lads were doing so well this year, I had a few chats with a few coaches, a few of the actual playing squad and everybody seemed keen to get me on board.\\\"\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch highlights of all the weekend's URC action on Against the Head, RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player, 8pm    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2381, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4118519433001234e-15, \"text\": \"URC\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 2413, \"end\": 2417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"score\": 0.9994238889060038, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c92\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c92\"}, {\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2478, \"end\": 2501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 2503, \"end\": 2510, \"title\": \